<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Khawvel thihna gam himah leh;
 Van chuh hinna gam ahi;
 Khawvel kikhenna himah leh,
 Van kituok khawmna ahi,
 I ngaih, lungdeih te I khena,
 Pham ngaia lu i su'n hin,
 Van khawpi nuom gal dawn hiting,
 Lungkham banna'n mang hitiu.

[V2]
 Nitin tungthak ana tuok ui
 A kipahnau a pung zel;
 Thih leh kikhen a lau ta puou,
 Nawp tawplo ding a chang ui.

[V3]
 2. Melma huoi sie thihna lal in,
 Sung tin naubang a kah sak;
 Kingaisie chuom um diek puoi tiu,
 Kuomah um dem ding um lo;
 Pathien hinna siemtu khan le,
 A Chapa lu a su'n kha,
 Mahleh van khuo ei tun zaw a,
 Guolpha'n ngai zaw mai hitiu,

[V4]
 3. I nu, I pa I guol ngaihte,
 I u, I nau I chate;
 Nupa'n le thihna'n a khen a,
 Lungkham banna ding umlo,
 Pathien Cha thihna zopa leh,
 Thih lungmuonna neitu chu;
 Bel in kulhpi'n mang hiting un,
 Lungmuong takin um hitiu.</lyrics>
<title>Van Khawpi Gel In</title>
</song>